el's%20resignation%20was%20notified%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20added%20that%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20two%20appointments%20of%20election%20commissioners%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20made%20against%20one%2C%20as%20anticipated%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20March%2015%20notice%2C%20the%20sources%20said%2C%20refers%20to%20the%20postponed%20meeting%20of%20the%20committee%20that%20was%20to%20be%20held%20on%20March%207%20to%20fill%20the%20vacancy%20created%20by%20the%20retirement%20of%20Pandey%2C%20who%20demitted%20office%20on%20February%2014%20on%20attaining%20the%20age%20of%2065%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20before%20the%20poll%20panel%20is%20expected%20to%20announce%20the%20schedule%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Goel%20resigned%20on%20Friday%20morning.%20His%20resignation%20was%20accepted%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20on%20Saturday%20and%20the%20Union%20Law%20Ministry%20issued%20a%20notification%20to%20announce%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20leaves%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20as%20the%20sole%20member%20of%20the%20poll%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20search%20committee%20under%20Union%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%2C%20and%20comprising%20the%20Home%20secretary%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20secretary%2C%20will%20first%20prepare%20two%20separate%20panels%20of%20five%20names%20each%20for%20the%20two%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20selection%20committee%20headed%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20name%20two%20persons%20for%20appointment%20as%20election%20commissioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%20selection%20committee%20could%20meet%20either%20on%20March%2013%20or%2014%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20convenience%20of%20the%20members%2C%20and%20the%20appointments%20were%20likely%20by%20March%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20a%20new%20law%20on%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20and%20election%20commissioners%20came%20into%20force%20recently%2C%20the%20election%20commissioners%20were%20appointed%20by%20the%20president%20on%20the%20government's%20recommendation%20and%2C%20as%20per%20custom%2C%20the%20senior-most%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClause%202%20of%20Article%20324%20of%20the%20Constitution%20states%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20shall%20consist%20of%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20and%20such%20number%20of%20other%20election%20commissioners%2C%20if%20any%2C%20as%20the%20president%20may%20from%20time%20to%20time%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20questions%20on%20the%20reasons%20behind%20Goel's%20resignation%2C%20the%20sources%20said%20he%20might%20have%20resigned%20due%20to%20personal%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20rejected%20suggestions%20that%20there%20were%20differences%20between%20Goel%20and%20Kumar%2C%20saying%20records%20of%20internal%20communication%2C%20minutes%20and%20decisions%20show%20there%20was%20no%20dissent%20recorded%20by%20Goel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20seasoned%20bureaucrats%20brainstorm%20on%20an%20issue%2C%20there%20are%20bound%20to%20be%20differences%20in%20opinion%20and%20perception.%20These%20cannot%20be%20described%20as%20differences%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoel%2C%20who%20tendered%20his%20resignation%20on%20Friday%20morning%2C%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20crucial%20meeting%20between%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20top%20home%20ministry%20and%20railways%20officials%20to%20firm%20up%20the%20deployment%20and%20the%20movement%20of%20central%20forces%20across%20India%20for%20poll%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoel%20was%20a%201985-batch%20IAS%20officer%20of%20the%20Punjab%20cadre.%20He%20had%20joined%20the%20Election%20Commission%20in%20November%202022.%20His%20tenure%20was%20until%20December%205%2C%202027%2C%20and%20he%20would%20have%20become%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20after%20incumbent%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20retired%20next%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%20Lavasa%20had%20resigned%20as%20election%20commissioner%20in%20August%202020.%20He%20had%20given%20dissent%20notes%20on%20various%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20violation%20decisions%20taken%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20during%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%2C%20the%20commission%20had%20only%20a%20chief%20election%20commissioner.%20It%20currently%20consists%20of%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20and%20two%20election%20commissioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20additional%20commissioners%20were%20first%20appointed%20on%20October%2016%2C%201989%2C%20but%20their%20tenures%20lasted%20till%20January%201%2C%201990.%20Later%2C%20on%20October%201%2C%201993%2C%20two%20additional%20election%20commissioners%20were%20appointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20a%20multi-member%20Election%20Commission%20has%20been%20in%20operation%20since%20then%2C%20with%20decisions%20made%20by%20a%20majority%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710093600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2F51qsbfd_election-commission-reuters_625x300_05_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-to-chair-key-meet-to-appoint-2-election-commissioners-on-march-15-5212610%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20prime%20minister-chaired%20high-powered%20committee%20will%20meet%20on%20March%2015%20to%20finalise%20the%20names%20of%20new%20election%20commissioners%2C%20top%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-to-chair-key-meet-to-appoint-2-election-commissioners-on-march-15-5212610%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.c