20the%20Viksit%20Bharat%20Ambassador%20Artist%20Workshop%20on%20Sunday%20and%20appreciated%20the%20event%20for%20showcasing%20the%20aspirations%20of%20people%20for%20a%20'Viksit%20Bharat'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20organised%20at%20the%20Purana%20Qila%20by%20the%20National%20Gallery%20of%20Modern%20Art%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Lalit%20Kala%20Akademi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStopped%20by%20at%20the%20%23ViksitBharatAmbassador%20Artist%20Workshop%20at%20Purana%20Qila%20today.%20Commend%20%40ngma_delhiand%20%40LalitKalaLKA%20for%20organizing.%20Pleased%20to%20see%20the%20various%20expressions%20of%20Viksit%20Bharat%20through%20the%20medium%20of%20art.%20%23ModiKiGuarantee%20was%20the%20underlying%20message%20that%20the%20country%20agrees%20with%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EStopped%20by%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FViksitBharatAmbassador%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ViksitBharatAmbassador%3C%2Fa%3E%20Artist%20Workshop%20at%20Purana%20Qila%20today.%20Commend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fngma_delhi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ngma_delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLalitKalaLKA%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40LalitKalaLKA%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20organizing.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPleased%20to%20see%20the%20various%20expressions%20of%20Viksit%20Bharat%20through%20the%20medium%20of%20art.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FModiKiGuarantee%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ModiKiGuarantee%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20underlying%20message%20that%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FyTH48shujV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FyTH48shujV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20S.%20Jaishankar%20(Modi%20Ka%20Parivar)%20(%40DrSJaishankar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrSJaishankar%2Fstatus%2F1766774996071014464%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20reporters%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20should%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20experience%20the%20diversity%20of%20India.%20Our%20target%20during%20the%20G20%20was%20that%20international%20events%20should%20not%20be%20limited%20to%20the%20national%20capital%20and%20should%20be%20taken%20across%20the%20country.%20When%20we%20talk%20about%20Viksit%20Bharat%20it%20means%20that%20the%20impact%20of%20India%20in%20the%20world%20increases%20and%20for%20that%2C%20it%20is%20important%20for%20everyone%20to%20know%20about%20Bharat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20great%20initiative.%20I%20saw%20the%20aspirations%20of%20people%20here.%20I%20can%20also%20see%20the%20strong%20impact%20of%20Chandrayaan.%20Modi%20ji%20and%20Chandrayaan%20are%20always%20on%20people's%20minds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20opened%20up%20on%20the%20various%20aspects%20of%20'Viksit%20Bharat'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20multiple%20aspects%20of%20Viksit%20Bharat.%20We%20consider%20ourselves%20as%20a%20civilizational%20state.%20We%20aspire%20to%20become%20a%20leading%20power%2C%20become%20a%20permanent%20member%20of%20the%20UNSC.%20We%20are%20the%20most%20populous%20country.%20On%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20we%20are%20at%20fifth%2C%20but%20will%20soon%20become%20third%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20also%20hailed%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20free%20trade%20pact%20and%20said%20that%20it%20reflects%20a%20new%20way%20of%20furthering%20international%20economic%20collaboration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Free%20Trade%20Association%20is%20a%20trade%20organisation%20and%20free%20trade%20area%20consisting%20of%20four%20European%20states-%20Iceland%2C%20Liechtenstein%2C%20Norway%20and%20Switzerland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20great%20day%20for%20India's%20partnership%20with%20Iceland%2C%20Liechtenstein%2C%20Norway%20and%20Switzerland.%20Congratulate%20my%20colleague%20CIM%20%40PiyushGoyal%20on%20this%20achievement.%20The%20India-EFTA%20Trade%20%26amp%3B%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement%20(TEPA)%20signed%20today%20is%20a%20bold%20achievement.%20It%20reflects%20a%20new%20way%20of%20furthering%20international%20economic%20collaboration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20held%20meetings%20with%20his%20counterparts%20from%20Liechtenstein%20and%20Iceland%20during%20the%20India-EFTA%20meeting%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHappy%20to%20reconnect%20with%20FM%20%40DominiqueHasler%20of%20Liechtenstein%20during%20the%20India-EFTA%20meeting%20today.%20Value%20our%20regular%20interactions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGood%20meeting%20with%20FM%20%40Bjarni_Ben%20of%20Iceland%20on%20India-EFTA%20meeting%20sidelines.%20Discussed%20new%20areas%20of%20collaboration%2C%20investment%20and%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EAM%20said%20in%20a%20subsequent%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%20EFTA%20has%20committed%20to%20promote%20investments%20to%20increase%20the%20stock%20of%20foreign%20direct%20investments%20by%20USD%20100%20billion%20in%20India%20in%20the%20next%2015%20years%2C%20and%20to%20facilitate%20the%20generation%20of%201%20million%20direct%20employment%20in%20India%2C%20through%20such%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20India%20has%20been%20working%20on%20a%20Trade%20and%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement%20(TEPA)%20with%20EFTA%20countries%20comprising%20Switzerland%2C%20Iceland%2C%20Norway%20and%20Liechtenstein%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20