r%20Success%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Player-of-the-Series%20award%20winner%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20on%20Saturday%20attributed%20his%20overwhelming%20success%20in%20the%20five-Test%20rubber%20against%20England%20to%20his%20uninhibited%20approach%20while%20opening%20the%20innings.%20Jaiswal%20ended%20the%20series%20with%20712%20runs%20with%20two%20hundreds%20and%20three%20fifties%2C%20averaging%2089%20and%20striking%20at%2080.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20thinking%20if%20I%20can%20take%20a%20bowler%20down%2C%20I%20will%20take%20him%20down.%20That's%20the%20plan%20and%20there%20was%20no%20backing%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jaiswal%20during%20the%20post-series%20presentation.%20However%2C%20the%20left-hander%2C%20who%20became%20only%20the%20second%20Indian%20to%20score%20over%20700%20runs%20in%20a%20series%20after%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%2C%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20keep%20his%20feet%20planted%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20enjoyed%20the%20series.%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20take%20it%20one%20game%20at%20a%20time%20and%20always%20thinking%20of%20how%20I%20can%20contribute%20to%20my%20team%20so%20that%20I%20can%20keep%20the%20team%20in%20a%20winning%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20too%20reminded%20Jaiswal%20of%20the%20need%20to%20remain%20humble%20and%20focussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20got%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%2C%20but%20it's%20amazing%20to%20be%20in%20this%20position.%20When%20a%20guy's%20got%20talent%20like%20that%20who%20can%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20bowlers%20from%20the%20word%20go%2C%20there%20will%20be%20lots%20of%20challenges%20going%20forward.%20He%20is%20a%20tough%20guy%20and%20loves%20the%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20trying%20to%20keep%20ball%20on%20good%20length%3A%20Kuldeep%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%20was%20adjudged%20player%20of%20the%20match%20for%20his%20seven-wicket%20haul%20and%20a%20feisty%2030%20down%20the%20order%20that%20helped%20India%20stretch%20the%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20left-arm%20wrist%20spinner%20said%20he%20was%20just%20trying%20to%20keep%20the%20ball%20on%20a%20good%20length%20throughout%20his%20spells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20focus%20on%20keeping%20it%20on%20a%20good%20length%20and%20that%20is%20very%20important%20for%20a%20spinner%20in%20this%20format.%20I%20was%20not%20thinking%20too%20much%20about%20what%20the%20batter%20was%20trying%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20picked%20the%20wickets%20of%20Ben%20Stokes%20at%20Ranchi%20and%20Zak%20Crawley%20here%20as%20his%20favourite%20dismissals%20from%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20bowled%20well%20in%20Ranchi.%20The%20wicket%20was%20slow%20and%20the%20way%20I%20used%20the%20drift%20over%20there%20was%20fantastic.%20I%20liked%20the%20Stokes%20wicket%20in%20Ranchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20liked%20the%20Crawley%20wicket%20here%20(Dharamsala)%2C%20that%20was%20a%20beautiful%20ball.%20I%20really%20liked%20my%20rhythm%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20bowled%20England%20captain%20Stokes%20with%20a%20delivery%20that%20spun%20in%20from%20off-stump%20while%20right-hander%20Crawley%20got%20castled%20by%20his%20stock%20ball%20that%20turned%20in%20sharply%20from%20the%20fifth-stump%20line%20to%20disturb%20his%20stumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20heaped%20praise%20on%20Kuldeep's%20work%20ethics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20potential%20and%20when%20the%20chips%20were%20down%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20(here)%2C%20he%20bowled%20really%20well.%20He%20came%20back%20and%20worked%20at%20NCA%20after%20his%20injury.%20He%20is%20putting%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%20and%20the%20most%20pleasing%20thing%20was%20his%20(improved)%20batting%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20be