20foster%20son%20to%20seek%20support%20from%20central%20parties.%20Elections%20are%20ahead.%20We%20are%20ready%20to%20fight%20against%20the%20alliance.%20YSRCP%20will%20stand%20with%20weaker%20sections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20on%20the%20TDP%20chief%20came%20at%20his%20party's%20huge%20show%20of%20strength%20--%20the%20fourth%20Siddham%20(Ready%20for%20polls)%20cadre%20meet%20at%20the%20Bapatla%20district's%20Addanki.%20The%20meet%20is%20being%20attended%20by%20lakhs%20of%20party%20workers%20from%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu%2C%20who%20had%20marched%20out%20of%20the%20NDA%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20made%20a%20U-turn%20yesterday%2C%20sealing%20a%20fresh%20deal%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20Jana%20Sena%20Party%20signed%20up%20with%20the%20NDA%20to%20contest%20the%20coming%20simultaneous%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20chief%20has%20been%20relegated%20to%20the%20fringes%20of%20state%20politics%20after%20his%20party's%20rout%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Mr%20Reddy's%20YSR%20Congress%20in%202019.%20Over%20the%20recent%20months%2C%20he%20has%20been%20under%20the%20lens%20of%20Central%20investigation%20agencies%20and%20even%20got%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20corruption%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20return%20to%20the%20NDA%20fold%20is%20expected%20to%20give%20the%20BJP%20a%20much%20sought-after%20shot-in-the-arm%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeen%20to%20find%20a%20toehold%20in%20southern%20states%20other%20than%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20seeking%20alliances%20with%20local%20parties.%20Its%20efforts%20are%20yet%20to%20bear%20fruit%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20questions%20whether%20its%20alliance%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20will%20have%20the%20desired%20effect%20at%20the%20hustings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20state%20polls%2C%20the%20YSRCP%20had%20bagged%20151%20seats%20in%20the%20175-member%20Assembly%2C%20and%20polled%2049.95%20per%20cent%20of%20votes%20%E2%80%93%2010%20per%20cent%20more%20than%20the%20TDP%2C%20which%20could%20only%20bag%2023%20seats.%20Actor%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20Jana%20Sena's%20debut%20was%20less%20than%20sterling%20with%20just%20a%20single%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20won%20four%20assembly%20seats%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20TDP%20in%202014%2C%20failed%20to%20win%20any..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20voting%20trend%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%202019%20had%20followed%20the%20same%20pattern.%20The%20YSRCP%2C%20which%20won%2022%20of%20the%2025%20parliamentary%20seats%2C%20polled%2049.15%20per%20cent%20votes.%20The%20TDP%20secured%2039.59%20per%20cent%20and%20bagged%20only%20three%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710080040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fsqbs4j24_jagan-reddy-chandrababu-naidu_625x300_10_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frusted-cycle-jagan-mohan-reddys-swipe-at-chandrababu-naidu-5212824%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%2C%20peeved%20with%20the%20alliance%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20Jana%20Sena%20Party%2C%20today%20said%20Mr%20Naidu's%20cycle%20is%20%26quot%3Brusted%26quot%3B%20and%20so%20he%20is%20seeking%20support%20from%20other%20parties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frusted-cycle-jagan-mohan-reddys-swipe-at-chandrababu-naidu-5212824%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frusted-cycle-jagan-mohan-reddys-swipe-at-chandrababu-naidu-5212824%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frusted-cycle-jagan-mohan-reddys-swipe-at-chandrababu-na