lization%2F%5C%22%3Eiron%2C%20copper%2C%20sand%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20everything%20else%E2%80%94including%20more%20coal%20and%20petroleum.%20Petroleum%20made%20it%20possible%20to%20fly%20passenger%20(or%20war)%20planes%2C%20connecting%20(or%20killing)%20people%20around%20the%20world%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20oil-based%20economy%20allows%20labor%2C%20capital%2C%20raw%20materials%2C%20and%20goods%20to%20move%20more%20rapidly%20along%20much%20the%20same%20pathways%20that%20were%20established%20during%20the%20centuries%20of%20European%20colonialism%3A%20materials%20and%20labor%20extracted%20from%20the%20Global%20South%20accumulate%20their%20benefits%20in%20the%20Global%20North%20faster%20than%20ever.%20Those%20pathways%20are%20kept%20open%20by%20oil-guzzling%2C%20industrialised%20militaries.%20Oil%2C%20itself%2C%20is%20also%20the%20source%20of%20huge%20quantities%20of%20cheap%20raw%20materials%20that%20further%20bolster%20industrialism%20by%20providing%20wholly%20novel%20materials%2C%20now%20essential%20to%20our%20lives%3A%20plastics%2C%20coatings%2C%20lubricants%2C%20solvents%2C%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20dyes%2C%20textiles%2C%20and%20more.%20And%20it%20does%20this%20at%20a%20cost%20unmatchable%20by%20any%20other%20material%20or%20process%20available%20on%20Earth.%20It%20is%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20the%20industrial%20economy.%20And%20the%20control%20of%20its%20production%2C%20distribution%2C%20and%20acquisition%20is%20a%20principle%20driver%20of%20modern%20geopolitics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10113314%2FNHQ202211160200large.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10113314%2FNHQ202211160200large.j