%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F343768755_The_Resource-Limited_Plateau_in_Global_Conventional_Oil_Production_Analysis_and_Consequences%5C%22%3Enot%20decades%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Without%20cheap%20oil%20to%20help%20build%20and%20power%20mining%20operations%2C%20access%20to%20coal%20and%20gas%20would%20also%20be%20diminished%2C%20the%20necessary%20rate%20and%20scale%20rendered%20economically%E2%80%94if%20not%20also%20logistically%E2%80%94unfeasible%20using%20other%20power%20sources.%20Continuing%20to%20increase%20our%20dependency%20on%20these%20fossils%20in%20any%20way%20makes%20literally%20no%20Earthly%20sense.%20We%20must%20instead%20imagine%20a%20system%20that%20moves%20away%20from%20burning%20fossils%2C%20altogether%2C%20rap%C2%A0idly%20and%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20586px)%2085vw%2C%20586px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112734%2FCarbon-Budgets-2023.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22586%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112734%2FCarbon-Budgets-2023.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112734%2FCarbon-Budgets-2023-300x211.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112734%2FCarbon-Budgets-2023-1024x721.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700959%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22413%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20rate%20at%20which%20we%20must%20phase%20out%20fossil%20fuel%20sources%20and%20adjust%20land-use%20practices%20for%20a%2067%25%20chance%20of%20limiting%20global%20warming%20thresholds%20of%201.5%C2%BAC%20(green)%2C%201.7%C2%BAC%20(blue)%2C%20or%202.0%C2%BAC%20red.%20Chart%3A%20Friedlingstein%20et%20al%202023%20(https%3A%2F%2Fessd.copernicus.org%2Farticles%2F15%2F5301%2F2023%2Fessd-15-5301-2023.html)%3B%20Global%2