%20%E2%80%98clean%E2%80%99%20Indian%20industrial%20economy.%20But%20despite%20all%20the%20%E2%80%98hope%E2%80%99%20elites%20declaim%20around%20%E2%80%98greening%E2%80%99%20our%20energy%20systems%2C%20we%20intuitively%20understand%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20way%20to%20have%20the%20%E2%80%98developed%2C%E2%80%99%20capitalist-consumerist%20economy%20without%20breaking%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20all%20the%20%E2%80%98renewable%E2%80%99%20energy%E2%80%94which%20is%20delivered%20to%20us%20only%20through%20installations%20that%20are%20%3Cem%3Enot%20at%20all%20renewable%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20%3Cem%3Emust%20be%20built%20and%20re-built%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20every%20few%20decades%E2%80%94thus%20far%20deployed%20haven%E2%80%99t%20begun%20to%20reduce%20our%20fossil%20fuel%20consumption.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fourworldindata.org%2Fgrapher%2Felectricity-prod-source-stacked%5C%22%3Eonly%20added%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20our%20overall%20energy%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20581px)%2085vw%2C%20581px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112945%2Fglobal-energy-substitution.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22581%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112945%2Fglobal-energy-substitution.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112945%2Fglobal-energy-substitution-300x212.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112945%2Fglobal-energy-substitution-1024x723.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700960%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22410%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERenewable%20energy%20sources%20haven%E2%80%99t%20reduced%20our%20demand%20for%20combustible%20fossils.%20They%20have%20only%20allowed%20us%20to%20increase%20our%20overall%20energy%20consumptio