s%20mothers%20and%20young%20daughters%20of%20India!%20You%20are%20now%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20dream%20in%20the%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMothers%20and%20youngsters%20are%20the%20new%20MY%20(Muslims%20and%20Yadavs)%20factor%20%E2%80%93%20a%20glorious%20combo%20whose%20collective%20votes%20shall%20bring%20a%20massive%20victory%20for%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20version%20of%20MY%20pales%20before%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMotherhood%20and%20youth%20have%20always%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20exquisite%20poems%2C%20sculptures%2C%20and%20paintings%2C%20mostly%20created%20by%20males.%20The%20impact%20of%20these%20timeless%20works%20of%20art%20is%20strong.%20Under%20slogans%20about%20women%20being%20%E2%80%98Shakti%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20youth%20being%20our%20collective%20future%2C%20several%20unexamined%20assumptions%20have%20always%20gone%20undebated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20why%20do%20images%20of%20young%20men%20predominate%20whenever%20the%20youth%20of%20India%20is%20being%20discussed%3F%20Why%20are%20young%20women%20projected%20as%20part%20of%20a%20total%20identity%20package%20labelled%20as%20mothers%20of%20the%20future%2C%20who%20will%20raise%20wonderful%20sons%20to%20serve%20Mother%20India%3F%20Is%20a%20young%20mother%2C%20who%20mostly%20spends%20all%20her%20days%20and%20nights%20caring%20for%20her%20children%2C%20isolated%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20and%20well-paid%20jobs%2C%20the%20most%20enviable%20soul%20upon%20the%20Earth%3F%20No%20one%20pauses%20to%20check%20this%20for%20a%20fact%20with%20MY-2%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20336px)%2085vw%2C%20336px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22336%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22410%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mysterious%20assumption%20is%20that%20our%20young%20virtuous%20mothers%20by%20their%20very%20definition%20are%20selfless.%20So%2C%20raising%20children%20is%20its%20own%20reward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20men%20fall%20under%20another%20category%20.%20They%20provide%20the%20seed%20and%20move%20on%20to%20work%20leaving%20the%20mother%20to%20care%20for%20the%20progeny.%20If%20asked%20why%20it%20must%20be%20so.%20The%20standard%20answer%20is%2C%20%E2%80%98Shall%20I%20leave%20my%20job%20then%3F%20Who%20will%20put%20food%20on%20the%20table%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20are%20great%20because%20they%20set%20men%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20underlying%20assumption%20is%20that%20a%20mother%E2%80%99s%20love%20is%20unconditional.%20She%20only%20gives%2C%20never%20demands%20anything%20in%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20talk%20sense%20for%20once%20around%20MY%20as%20it%20really%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20memories%20we%20all%20have%20of%20warmth%2C%20security%2C%20sensual%20tenderness%2C%20and%20being%20nourished%20come%20indeed%20from%20our%20mothers.%20But%20what%20is%20equally%20true%20is%20that%20as%20children%20turn%20into%20youthful%20creatures%2C%20intense%20feelings%20and%20shows%20of%20affection%20peter%20out.%20Most%20youngsters%2C%20especially%20sons%2C%20at%20some%20point%20begin%20to%20find%20mothers%E2%80%99%20love%20chokingly%20possessive.%20There%20are%20scores%20of%20jokes%20about%20whiny%20snooping%20mothers%20who%20rub%20your%20noses%20in%20guilt%20and%20need%20unstinted%20attention.%20This%20is%20also%20less%20visible%20but%20true%20in%20the%20case%20of%20young%20daughters.%20As%20they%20turn%20teenagers%2C%20mothers%20seem%20to%20them%20like%20gloomy%20prophets%20talking%20endlessly%20of%20male%20predators%20and%20the%20drudgery%20of%20a%20married%20woman%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20daughters%2C%20whose%20thoughts%20are%20turning%20into%20thoughts%20of%20romantic%20love%2C%20mothers%E2%80%99%20quips%20sound%20irritating%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20Frank%20talk%20between%20mothers%20and%20young%20daughters%20about%20love%2C%20sex%2C%20needs%20for%20privacy%20is%20carefully%20pared%20down.%20And%20mothers%20deem%20it%20fine%20for%20family%20males%20to%20chaperone%20young%20daughters%20and%2For%20monitor%20their%20outings%2C%20mobiles%2C%20and%20reading%20material%2C%20which%20they%20consider%20totally%20acceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heterosexual%20version%20of%20motherhood%20in%20traditional%20Indian%20families%20is%20supported%20by%20the%20presently%20dominant%20political%20ideology%2C%20and%20demands%20that%2C%20as%20girls%2C%20we%20transfer%20our%20feelings%20of%20dependency%2C%20sensuality%2C%20and%20mutuality%20to%20the%20male%20authority%20in%20control%20of%20that%20particular%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20few%20realise%2C%20deepens%20the%20rift%20between%20young%20women%20and%20older%20ones%20further.%20It%20is%20not%20surprising%2C%20therefore%2C%20that%20eminent%20women%20who%20have%20come%20up%20in%20the%20world%2C%20mostly%20credit%20fathers%20for%20encouraging%20and%20mentoring%20them.%20Men%20get%20the%20credit%20when%20daughters%20top%20the%20merit%20lists%2C%20but%20mothers%20mostly%20appear%20as%20shy%20withdrawn%20figures%20feeding%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20toppers%20or%20smiling%20wordlessly%20on%20our%20TV%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20constant%20belittling%20of%20ageing%20mothers%20and%20the%20ambitions%20of%20young%20daughters%20automatically%20promotes%20notions%20of%20aggrandisement%20of%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20unquestioned%20supremacy%20within%20families%20and%20politics%20helps%20young%20men%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20and%20makes%20them%20idolise%20the%20father%20and%20lends%20them%20a%20positive%20assertive%20self%20image%20girls%20are%20denied.%20Male%20ambition%20is%20deemed%20admirable%20and%20assertiveness%20is%20valued%20as%20a%20virtue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20young%20girls%2C%20when%20they%20seek%20to%20empower%20themselves%2C%20suddenly%20everything%20becomes%20a%20cautious%20%E2%80%9Cask%20your%20brothers%2C%20fathers%2C%20or%20uncles%20for%20guidance.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ESab%20kuch%20papa%20(or%20bhai%20or%20uncles)%20se%20pooch%20kar%20karna%20hai!%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20before%20the%20ruling%20male%20cabals%20lump%20MY-2%20as%20a%20faceless%20body%20of%20votes%2C%20and%20promise%20them%20free%20education%2C%20cheaper%20cooking%20gas%2C%20money%20in%20the%20bank%20and%20free%20laptops%2C%20they%20need%20to%20realise%20this%20alone%20cannot%20lead%20to%20empowerment.%20Young%20daughters%20know%2C%20as%20they%20grow%2C%20it%20is%20the%20mother%20who%20is%20sold%20to%20her%20as%20her%20role%20model.%20But%20how%20many%20of%20them%20wish%20to%20sacrifice%20their%20independence%20and%20free%20will%20to%20the%20men%20in%20their%20lives%3A%20father%2C%20husband%2C%20employers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20undeniable%20rise%20in%20crimes%20against%20working%20women%20in%20streets%20and%20offices%2C%20the%20word%20in%20the%20street%20is%20working%20women%20are%20paying%20for%20their%20ambitions.%20Young%20working%20wives%20risk%20constant%20social%20disapprobation%20and%20even%20ostracisation%20for%20being%20different%20to%20other%20compliant%20%3Cem%3Ebahus%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CLadki%20ho%20ke%20bhi%20apne%20ko%20bahut%20bada%20samjhati%20hai!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20mother%20and%20daughter%2C%20my%20writer%20mother%20and%20I%20always%20exchanged%20unspoken%20knowledge%20about%20the%20impending%20erosion%20of%20a%20mother%E2%80%99s%20authority%20as%20a%20parent%20as%20career%20choices%20loomed.%20And%20I%20saw%20time%20and%20again%20how%20the%20family%20would%20stand%20by%20the%20father%20and%20elder%20men%20to%20decide%20young%20girls%E2%80%99%20and%20mothers%E2%80%99%20work%20choices%20through%20an%20old%20list%20of%20dos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20created%20for%20daughters%20by%20traditional%20family%20men.%20But%20skilled%20manipulators%20that%20they%20were%2C%20the%20don%E2%80%99ts%20were%20transmitted%20through%20mothers%20and%20grandmothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShow%20me%20a%20woman%20in%20my%20generation%20who%2C%20when%20she%20obviously%20outshone%20other%20candidates%20for%20a%20good%20job%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20asked%20the%20appalling%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CIs%20your%20family%20okay%20with%20you%20working%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%20there%20has%20been%20progress%20and%20there%20is%20hope.%20Even%20decades%20ago%2C%20a%20subliminal%2C%20subversive%2C%20but%20preverbal%20knowledge%20passed%20between%20me%20and%20my%20mother%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20is%20so%20wrong!%E2%80%9D%20It%20was%20almost%20as%20though%20I%20was%20still%20within%20her%2C%20floating%20in%20the%20amniotic%20fluid.%20Many%20of%20my%20family%20opted%20for%20peace%20but%20my%20mother%20stood%20by%20me%20worried%20but%20firmly%20supportive%20of%20my%20silent%20refusal%20to%20bend%20my%20will%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20when%20I%20think%20of%20the%20impossible%20conditions%20under%20which%20my%20mother%20rose%20to%20be%20a%20literary%20figure%20in%20the%2060s%20in%20India%2C%20despite%20the%20impossible%20societal%20expectations%20of%20homemakers%2C%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20distaste%20for%20women%20performing%20on%20stage%2C%20his%20quiet%20rage%20at%20my%20mother%20occasionally%20travelling%20on%20her%20own%20to%20Lucknow%20and%20broadcasting%20her%20works%20on%20the%20AIR%2C%20my%20anger%20against%20her%20dissolves%20into%20sadness%20followed%20by%20a%20strange%20but%20ancient%20unexpurgated%20anger%20of%20a%20young%20daughter%3A%20Why%20was%20she%20so%20diffident%3F%20How%20could%20she%20make%20it%20sound%20to%20her%20children%20like%20a%20joke%20or%20just%20a%20prank%3F%20What%20would%20have%20happened%20if%20my%20mother%20had%20tried%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20mother%E2%80%9D%20like%20her%20female%20relatives%2C%20accepting%20the%20near%20impossible%20demands%20made%20on%20women%20of%20her%20generation%20and%20turned%20into%20an%20anxious%2C%20worrying%20puritanical%20keeper%20of%20her%20daughters%20and%20their%20virginity%20until%20good%20boys%20had%20been%20found%20for%20all%20of%20them%20by%20the%20men%20in%20the%20family%20and%20they%20went%20off%20to%20their%20%E2%80%9Cown%20house%E2%80%9D%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20want%20to%20laugh%20about%20those%20anxious%20days%2C%20but%20a%20part%20of%20me%20still%20refuses%20to%20forget%20a%20period%20when%20one%20felt%20unprotected%2C%20unmothered%20and%20alone%20in%20a%20male%20dominant%20media.%20I%20never%20forget%20before%20feminism%20formally%20entered%20working%20spaces%2C%20how%20transitory%2C%20fragmented%2C%20and%20wordless%20the%20world%20seemed%20to%20young%20women%20globally.%20The%20timeless%20stories%20of%20the%20mother%20and%20daughter%20bond%20and%20their%20forced%20separation%2C%20the%20price%20we%20paid%20for%20finding%20our%20own%20voice%20and%20vote.%20We%20have%20managed%20over%20time%20to%20claim%20our%20experience%20as%20underestimated%20paid%20workers%20and%20of%20mental%20and%20physical%20abuse%20as%20real%20and%20got%20many%20old%20laws%20revised%20and%20made%20more%20women-friendly.%20These%20are%20some%20of%20a%20million%20silent%20mutinies%20to%20be%20still%20recorded.%20So%20do%20not%20try%20to%20turn%20us%20into%20MY-2%20good%20Sirs%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20come%20a%20long%20way!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaakhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmrinal-pande%5C%22%3EMrinal%20Pande%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20s