ww.thebetterindia.com%2F298273%2Fsebi-consultation-paper-green-debt-securities-invest-in-sustainable-finance%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESEBI%3C%2Fa%3E)%20has%20published%20a%20consultation%20paper%20on%20easing%20the%20nominations%20for%20your%20Demat%20accounts%20and%20other%20securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20nomination%20is%20important%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncluding%20nominees%20in%20demat%20accounts%20is%20indispensable%20in%20ensuring%20the%20seamless%20transfer%20of%20securities%2C%20such%20as%20shares%2C%20bonds%2C%20and%20mutual%20funds%2C%20in%20the%20unfortunate%20event%20of%20the%20account%20holder%E2%80%99s%20demise.%20This%20vital%20step%20ensures%20that%20the%20transmission%20of%20these%20securities%20is%20smooth%20and%20without%20risks.%20Consequently%2C%20it%20shields%20the%20investments%20made%20by%20the%20account%20holder%20from%20the%20possibility%20of%20being%20lost%20or%20entangled%20in%20legal%20quagmires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20adding%20nominees%20to%20your%20accounts%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20simplifying%20matters%20for%20your%20beneficiaries%20%E2%80%94%20you%E2%80%99re%20also%20securing%20a%20brighter%2C%20more%20stable%20future%20for%20those%20you%20hold%20dear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fd3mygWN85TA%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fd3mygWN85TA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20the%20consultation%20paper%20by%20SEBI%20says%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consultation%20paper%20by%20SEBI%20encapsulates%20close%20to%20all%20the%20potential%20doubts%20you%20may%20have%20concerning%20the%20nomination%20process%20for%20securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20examining%20its%20contents%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20a%20consultation%20paper%20is%20a%20document%20meant%20to%20spark%20discussion%20around%20policy%20proposals%20and%20ideas.%20Therefore%2C%20none%20of%20the%20points%20put%20forward%20by%20SEBI%20are%20binding%2C%20i.e.%20create%20a%20new%20law%20or%20policy.%20They%20are%20simply%20recommendations%20laid%20down%20for%20further%20conversation%20and%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20consultation%20paper%2C%20they%20broadly%20lay%20down%20three%20issues%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20the%20nomination%20process%20apply%20to%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20role%20of%20nominees%20with%20respect%20to%20legal%20heirs%20and%20wills%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20method%20of%20appointing%20nominees%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20very%20clearly%20underscored%20that%20nomination%20is%20an%20%E2%80%98entirely%20optional%20process%E2%80%99.%20The%20recommendation%20SEBI%20makes%20is%20that%20in%20a%20single%20person-held%20demat%20account%2C%20a%20clear%20declaration%20be%20made%20that%20they%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20assign%20a%20nominee.%20This%20is%20simply%20a%20measure%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20procedural%20ease%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20thing%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20before%20reading%20the%20paper%20is%20the%20distinction%20between%20nominees%20and%20legal%20heirs%2C%20which%20can%20often%20be%20a%20point%20of%20confusion%20for%20a%20layperson.%20As%20highlighted%20by%20various%20financial%20experts%20and%20publications%2C%20nominees%20are%20not%20legal%20heirs%20to%20the%20securities.%20They%20are%20simply%20temporary%20custodians%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20ensuring%20the%20securities%20are%20correctly%20transferred%20to%20the%20legal%20heirs%2C%20as%20per%20a%20will%20or%20law.%20They%20are%20akin%20to%20an%20executor%20of%20a%20will%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20but%20for%20a%20specific%20asset%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20paper%2C%20SEBI%20provides%20suggestions%20on%20processes%20for%20how%20nominees%20can%20be%20appointed%20and%20how%20they%20must%20act.%20Nominees%20can%20be%20appointed%20through%20digital%20methods%20for%20ease%2C%20however%2C%20safety%20is%20kept%20in%20mind%20in%20this%20process%20as%20well%20by%20ensuring%20the%20requirement%20of%20a%20digital%20signature%20or%20Aadhaar-based%20eSigns.%20One%20needs%20to%20provide%20identification%20of%20the%20proposed%20nominee(s)%20as%20well.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20physical%20nomination%20through%20thumb%20impressions%20and%20verification%20also%20continues%20to%20be%20proposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20provides%20various%20scenarios%2C%20such%20as%20sole%20accounts%2C%20joint%20accounts%2C%20simultaneous%20deaths%20of%20account%20holders%20among%20others%2C%20and%20how%20a%20nominee%20will%20be%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20account%20for%20the%20next%20steps%20in%20each%20case.%20It%20also%20lays%20down%20which%20legal%20heirs%20are%20entitled%20to%20the%20securities%20in%20cases%20of%20joint%20accounts%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20read%20a%20more%20detailed%20summary%20of%20the%20paper%2C%20and%20provide%20your%20feedback%20on%20it%20by%208%20March%2C%202024%2C%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F48w8AwO%5C%22%3ECivis%20Platform%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivis%20is%20a%20civic-tech%20organisation%20that%20aggregates%20and%20simplifies%20draft%20laws%20and%20policies%20that%20are%20open%20for%20public%20feedback%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20making%20the%20process%20as%20simple%20for%20you%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consultation%20paper%20has%20been%20hosted%20with%20a%20summary%20that%20you%20can%20read%20in%20an%20accessible%20format%2C%20in%20both%20English%20and%20Hindi%2C%20and%20give%20your%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20written%20by%20the%20team%20at%20Civis.vote%2C%20a%20non-profit%20platform%20that%20works%20to%20build%20dialogue%20between%20governments%20and%20citizens%2C%20using%20technology%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709561507000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fd3mygWN85TA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343865%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20thousands%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%20lying%20unclaimed%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20nominations%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20has%20put%20out%20a%20consultation%20paper%20on%20easing%20the%20nominee%20process%20for%20your%20Demat%20accounts%20and%20other%20securities%20in%20case%20of%20any%20adverse%20events.%20Here's%20what%20that%20means%20for%20you%20and%20the%20steps%20you%20can%20take%20to%20protect%20your%20assets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Civis%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343865%2Fsebisebi-consultation-paper-on-nominee-filing-and-protection-of-assets-demats-mutual-funds%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JetBlue%2C%20Spirit%20Ending%20%243.8%20Billion%20Merger%20Plan%20After%20Federal%20Judge%20Blocked